# Autarky v0.1 - The Ultimate Math Test
# Formula: ((10.5 * 2.0) + 14.0) / 2.0 - 5.0
# Expected Native & VM Result: 12.5

# The \init lambda catches the runner's starting argument
\init . 
    sub 
        (div 
            (add 
                (mul 10.5 2.0) 
                14.0
            ) 
            2.0
        ) 
        5.0